# 🧪 Practice Software Testing – Bug Hunting Project

## 📌 Overview

Manual testing project for a demo e-commerce website:
https://with-bugs.practicesoftwaretesting.com/

Focus: identifying functional bugs, UI issues, and usability problems in key user flows.

---

## 🎯 Scope

* Shopping cart
* Product pages
* Checkout & payment
* User profile
* Navigation & categories
* UI/UX & cross-browser testing

---

## 🧪 Approach

Exploratory testing supported by basic test scenarios.
Tested main user flows, edge cases, and error handling.

---

## 🐞 Bugs

Key issues found:

* Cart functionality errors (removal, totals)
* Payment gateway (404 error)
* Broken categories
* UI inconsistencies

➡️ See: **bug-report.md**

---

## 🌐 Environment

* Chrome, Firefox, Opera
* Windows 10

---

## 💡 Conclusion

Critical issues in checkout and cart significantly impact user experience and prevent successful purchases.

